{"tid":1679695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙控：將資本撤至增長及回報較高市場","createTime":"2019-10-28T10:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T10:55:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96da593eac93f633bd18cbba660ae33cac789570","tid":1679695,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1488651_1_L_20191028173133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1488651_1_L_20191028173133.jpg&h=238f040e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滙控臨時集團行政總裁祈耀年表示，要將資本轉投至增長及回報較高的市場，但詳情留待公布第4季業績時披露，又指要調整成本基礎以支持收入表現。<br />\n<br />\n他指，重整業務並非新鮮事，但與18個月前公布策略計劃時比較，經濟環境已有轉變，重整行動變得更為逼切，但承認扭轉業務的能力受限制。<br />\n<br />\n被問到集團會否在披露新策略前，就公布下任行政總裁人選，祈耀年說，目前並無詳情公布，重申聘任行政總裁需時6至12個月。"},{"pid":"585e3741ec9e69992fcf22cd00a6af2bc9aba0ce","tid":1679695,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"38cc6781219fb79cb1d406f10be0b1d413e8b8bd","tid":1679695,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎"},{"pid":"0de17191fbebcead91473be779e4349cd9d936c4","tid":1679695,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"借左4000億比人, 改口叫投資係佢身上? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52987d02d5825cdc55b090bd557ed234549ddf22","tid":1679695,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"盤數要幾肉酸至可以令今日斷崖式跌左$1.4<img sr